18
00:00:02,049 --> 00:00:09,189
fill the bottom chamber with fresh water just below the pressure valve. fill the filter basket

19
00:00:09,189 --> 00:00:12,650
with coffee powder and level it. place
the filter basket

20
00:00:12,650 --> 00:00:16,850
inside the bottom chamber. assemble the
pot.

21
00:00:16,850 --> 00:00:19,920
place it on the stove on medium heat for
a few minutes.

22
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:27,580
note that this does not work on an
induction stuff.

23
00:00:27,580 --> 00:00:32,690
when you hear the gurgling sound remove
from the stove. brew will be collected

24
00:00:32,690 --> 00:00:35,710
in the collecting chamber. pour the brew into a cup.

